{"type": "article", "id": 2206, "title": "像果冻杯的重力闹钟", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:28:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060522225376F53VxHNgsdb8AX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">美好的一天从清晨开始。这款名为“ Jelly ”的重力闹钟由设计团队 Style Pie 打造，设计灵感来源于果冻杯，可爱的时钟将唤回童心未泯的成年人对于纯真童年的美好回忆。Jelly 拥有最简单的线条与有趣的圆形滚动轮廓，时钟的表面十分平滑，按钮拥闹钟的盒盖隐藏在杯体内，轻轻一推便可启动闹钟的贪睡功能，闹钟会在重力的作用下自动滚到原位。如果将正面朝下则可直接关闭闹铃，十分方便而有趣。定价 78 元，</span><a href=\"http://item.taobao.com/item.htm?_u=b1558kk8db9&amp;id=40535065793\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134912ax3GAkuCKsBdclFe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261349132a1nM4AZtEWz3JYP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134913KSBe4jZEz7RO90CJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134914AHm6NT8dbRM4xYjf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}